items.name: Total Miner Wiki
items.title: Total Miner Wiki
items.headline: Come Join the Total Miner Wiki!
items.desc: We, miners, edit and discuss hot topics like the new update on the Xbox Indie Game Total Miner: Forge. Total Miner: Forge is a sandbox block style gane inspired by games like Minecraft and Infiniminer. The game includes a survival and creative modes. Anyone from casual to hardcore gamers cam freely express their imaginations in this wonderous gane. Feel free to check out our content and make conversations with our other miners. We are clear from trolls, and a small community. Total Miner is starting to become a hot topic in the Xbox Indie Games once again after the new update that was recently released. We appreciate newcomers and visitors who would like to come check us out. We're open to everyone... by the community for the community

items.name: CastleMiner Wiki
items.title: CastleMiner Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the CastleMiner Wikia!
items.desc: CastleMiner is an Xbox LIVE Indie game, developed by DigitalDNA Studios. It is currently available for 80 Microsoft Points, or $1 US currency. It is a game a lot like Minecraft, although you use your Xbox Avatar in the place of Minecraft avatars, and different features than Minecraft. You currently get unlimited blocks and you can unlock blocks by doing different tasks, similar to the 'Creative' mode in Minecraft. You can play online with you and up to 15 other people.

items.name: Castle Miner Z Wiki
items.title: Castle Miner Z Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the CastleMiner Z Wiki
items.desc: Welcome to the official Wiki for CastleMiner Z.  In the game you travel with your Avatar and your friends in a huge spanning and ever-changing world while defending yourself from the zombie horde. Mine the world for resources, to craft the weapons that you will need to survive. On the wiki you can find all information needed about the Xbox Live Indie Game -- from weapons and tools to tactics and enemies. Help out the Community any way you can by suggesting updates on blogs or adding honest information from the game CastleMiner Z.
